channel.title: Life-X PvP Dev team
channel.description:
Alright ill start off with saying, this server is going to be an Economy based PvP server, it still needs alot of work put into it but i know with the right dev team WE can do it. I only have a few tasks before i let people play it, but i have alot of updates in mind for after the release to keep it intresting for the players. have. Future updates to add in the game: Nietziot Quest Webclient Pk point shop Clan wars map data and full working clan wars Much More! Spots Needed: Server Programmer: Server Programmer: Junior Programmer: Asshole_rule Server Hoster: Asshole_rule Client Programmer (needs to be able to make a webclient please!): Web Developer:abdul Beta Tester(I'm very picky about these! make a very good application!): angelfallen Beta Tester ^: Here is the layout:
IRL Name : Age: MSN: Spot I want: Why do you want to join this dev team: Experience: Amount of time I will dedicate: Do you relize that if you are inactive or do not contribute to the team you CAN AND WILL be kicked out and your work deleted (yes/no): Other information you should know:
[IMG]http://i56.tinypic.com/122c0ew.jpg[/img] Though 508 map would be unique enough. [IMG]http://i54.tinypic.com/10z2u82.jpg[/img] Worked hard on adding these customs and still need to add some of them to item.cfg [IMG]http://i52.tinypic.com/hu2kuc.jpg[/img] These are some of the maps i've added, i plan on adding a nietziot quest so nietziot will come in handy and im already using godwars, just need a good purpose for jatiz. [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/24bs32f.jpg[/img] Heres some skillcapes, I didn't add these but it is a cool addition dont ya think? :p gives players a sense of accomplishment [URL=http://tinypic.com/r/28sabg7/7]View My Video[/URL] CREDITS TO DEMISE - I added this because its way more unique then adding these lame old commands and i love having whatever levels i want to pk with. You can be a pure, master, or zerker without making multiple accounts!
